marketinginformation: Keep an Eye on What Matters Most The Day/Night Network Cloud Camera (DCS-933L) delivers high-quality video for remote viewing on the mobile devices you already own. And with a built-in ICR filter and IR LEDs, you'll also get clear images in complete darkness to provide you with the ideal 24-hour monitoring solution. Integrated sound/motion-sensing technology detects changes within the camera's environment, triggering instant email alerts. Round the clock notification delivers an additional layer of security and confidence.
